rdCamp Montclair</a> in New Jersey, USA June 25 (in person)</li><li><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/13.1.0/72x72/1f1fa-1f1f8.png" alt="🇺🇸" class="wp-smiley" /> <a href="https://us.wordcamp.org/2022/">WordCamp US</a> in San Diego, California from September 9 to 11, 2022 (in person)</li></ul></li></ul>



