<p><strong>Jonny Harris</strong> <a href="https://twitter.com/thespacedmonkey/status/1499044349371371520">announced</a> that he has <a href="https://core.trac.wordpress.org/ticket/10886">merged a patch</a> into WordPress core for a 12-year-old ticket that &#8220;could have a massive effect on performance for custom pages.&#8221;</p>



